---
title: Grilled Shrimp "Paella" with Grilled Veggies and Lemon-Olive Relish
description: This elegant summer supper gets extra smoky flavour from cooking on the grill! This unexpected method for cooking rice is inspired by the open-air markets of Spain! We've shrunken our recipe down from a giant paella pan to suit the simple skillet.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paella-aux-crevettes-grillees-d9ec03fa.jpg
